21
00:01:08,950 --> 00:01:12,440
For example, as you'll see in the next lesson, when you make a submit,

22
00:01:12,440 --> 00:01:15,398
Git opens an editor for you to write a commit message.

23
00:01:15,398 --> 00:01:18,280
You want to just set this editor to whatever you prefer to use.
